        "title": "Fix bullet/list text clipping in chat (issue #636)",
        "body": "Markdown list rows used HStack (horizontal StackPanel), which measures children with infinite width. The paragraph TextBlock therefore never wrapped and long bullets got clipped by the chat bubble's max width.\r\n\r\nSwitch each list row to a 2-column Grid (Auto marker + Star content) so the content column receives a finite width and TextWrapping=Wrap works as intended.\r\n\r\nFix screenshot:\r\n<img width=\"1730\" height=\"1109\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e0d18952-f811-42fa-b534-38de86b07829\" />\r\n\r\nFixes #636",
